        <mxCell id="p2pa" value="PLANE A — On-behalf-of&lt;br&gt;Interactive agent runs AS the launching user&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;• creds injected per-run (NOT in prompt)&lt;br&gt;• A2A strips _credentials each hop&lt;br&gt;• run visible only to that user&lt;br&gt;• preflight-requires user integrations" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#d5e8d4;strokeColor=#82b366;align=left;verticalAlign=top;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="300" y="340" width="290" height="240" as="geometry"/></mxCell>
