        <mxCell id="p5risk" value="Residual risk:  HIGH (today)  →  MEDIUM (after Phase 0)  →  LOW (after Phase 3)" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#f5f5f5;strokeColor=#666666;fontStyle=1;align=center;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="40" y="64" width="1480" height="34" as="geometry"/></mxCell>

        <mxCell id="p5p0" value="PHASE 0 — Correctness gates   (MUST precede the broker · partly EXPLOITABLE NOW)&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;🟠 Authenticate + rate-limit /api/credentials/github + all write routes; kill dev-* bypass   ·   🟠 Bind user_id to verified JWT principal (ignore body)&lt;br&gt;🟠 Stop creds-in-prompt; deliver via agent_context   ·   🟠 A2A default-isolate + strip _credentials   ·   🟠 Least-priv Cloud Run runtime SA + internal ingress/IAP   ·   🟠 Wire kernel registry + FORGEOS_KERNEL_MODE=production" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#ffe6cc;strokeColor=#d79b00;align=left;verticalAlign=top;fontStyle=0;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="40" y="120" width="1480" height="120" as="geometry"/></mxCell>
        <mxCell id="p5p1" value="PHASE 1 — Foundation: identity + isolation&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;⬜ Google SSO/OIDC → JWT   ·   ⬜ forgeos login (device flow)   ·   ⬜ per-request namespace/tenant + RLS enforced   ·   ⬜ kill 'default' fallback + required-integration preflight&lt;br&gt;✅ partial: AuthUser/RBAC code exists (unwired) · A2A ACLs exist · kernel pipeline shape exists" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#dae8fc;strokeColor=#6c8ebf;align=left;verticalAlign=top;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="40" y="270" width="1480" height="110" as="geometry"/></mxCell>
        <mxCell id="p5p2" value="PHASE 2 — Credential Broker (separate service)&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;⬜ Broker service + own SA (token-creator isolated)   ·   ⬜ generalize per-user vault: GitHub (fix) · Workspace OAuth · GCP per-user SA impersonation&lt;br&gt;⬜ per-run injection + audit every mint   ·   ❗ DECIDE: GCP-OBO = SA impersonation vs true OAuth" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#e1d5e7;strokeColor=#9673a6;align=left;verticalAlign=top;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="40" y="410" width="1480" height="110" as="geometry"/></mxCell>
        <mxCell id="p5p3" value="PHASE 3 — Multi-project auditor (hardened-A2)&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;⬜ dedicated audit SA + CUSTOM read role   ·   ⬜ folder-level grants + allowlist   ·   ⬜ hard-exclude via IAM Deny + VPC-SC   ·   ⬜ external append-only audit sink&lt;br&gt;✅ auditor agent + notify__email tool exist today" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#d5e8d4;strokeColor=#82b366;align=left;verticalAlign=top;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="40" y="550" width="1480" height="110" as="geometry"/></mxCell>
        <mxCell id="p5p4" value="PHASE 4 — Defense-in-depth&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;⬜ A4 external auditor host   ·   ⬜ prompt-injection defense + HITL on dangerous tools   ·   ⬜ egress controls/proxy   ·   ⬜ Secret Manager CMEK + rotation   ·   ⬜ SIEM/alerting + break-glass   ·   ⬜ EU data-residency review" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#f5f5f5;strokeColor=#666666;align=left;verticalAlign=top;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="40" y="690" width="1480" height="100" as="geometry"/></mxCell>

